## Installation

```bash
uv add monzoh
```

## Quick Start

```python
from monzoh import MonzoClient

# Initialize client
client = MonzoClient()

# List accounts
accounts = client.accounts.list()

# Get account balance
balance = client.accounts.get_balance(account_id="acc_123")

# List transactions
transactions = client.transactions.list(account_id="acc_123")
```

